(245, 1, '2018-08-01 22:44:39', '2018-08-01 22:44:39', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 text-center\">\r\n<h1></h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"about_us\" style=\"font-size: 36px;\">ABOUT US</span></h1>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">The main goal of SBI Gaming is to allow people of similar interests, specifically in games, to get together and form a community. There is no focus on any particular game. We specialize in League of Legends and Hearthstone but are currently working towards hosting events for Overwatch, PUBG, CS:GO, Dota 2, and much more. Our wishes include promoting (competitive) eSports throughout UB, working on communication skills, and forming connections among gamers at the university. In order to work towards these goals, SBI Gaming hosts at least one or two events each month (not including December, January, and May), whether it be a LAN party, tournament, or even a casual board game night.</span>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n<h2 id=\"contact_us\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">CONTACT US</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Email: sliao3@buffalo.edu</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'SBI Gaming', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sbi-gaming', '', '', '2018-08-26 22:59:31', '2018-08-26 22:59:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?page_id=245', 0, 'page', '', 0),
