(443, 1, '2018-08-09 16:48:34', '2018-08-09 16:48:34', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"backgroundColor\":\"luminous-vivid-orange\",\"customFontSize\":26} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-luminous-vivid-orange-background-color\" style=\"font-size: 26px;\">Fall 2018 WAIVER WINDOW IS NOW OPEN, please visit the link Gallagherstudent.com to begin the domestic student medical insurance waiver. Gallagher Student Health has been contracted to handle the domestic waiver process. All question and concerns regarding the waiver process should be directed to Gallagher Student Health Customer Service: <br /><a href=\"https://www.gallagherstudent.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">www.Gallagherstudent.com</a></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"luminous-vivid-orange\",\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-background has-large-font-size has-luminous-vivid-orange-background-color\" style=\"text-align: center;\">International Student go to:<a href=\"http://healthinsurance.buffalo.edu/insuranceforms.html\">forms</a></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><header>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12\">\r\n<div class=\"intro-text\"><hr class=\"star-light\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<section id=\"portfolio\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> </div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 text-center\">\r\n<h1>STUDENT INSURANCE PLANS</h1>\r\n<hr class=\"star-primary\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<p><strong>Domestic Students</strong> <br />Sub Board I, Inc. has negotiated a plan with lower premium costs and lower co-pays for visits with Blue Cross and Blue Shield of WNY for the domestic students. Plan benefits are effective August 22 through August 21 of the following year. For details about the plan, links to find a participating provider, or to contact Blue Cross and Blue Shield of WNY about benefits,<a href=\"https://www.bcbswny.com/content/WNYHome.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> click here</a>. <br /><strong>All domestic waiver questions and concerns must be directed to: <a href=\"https://www.gallagherstudent.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.gallagherstudent.com</a> customer service at : <br />(877) 231-9757</strong> <br /><br /><strong>International Students/Scholars/OPT</strong> <br />International students, Scholars, and OPT students have a global insurance policy available to them, contracted by SUNY through GeoBlue. To search for a provider, get detailed plan benefits or to contact GeoBlue directly, <a href=\"https://www.geobluestudents.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">click here. </a>Students and scholars who are adequately insured may be able to waive the GeoBlue insurance plan by providing proof of comparable coverage. Restrictions and deadlines apply.<a href=\"http://healthinsurance.buffalo.edu/insuranceforms.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">  Click here to access the wavier packet.</a><br /><br /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 text-center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<h1>FALL 2018 INFORMATION IS COMING SOON</h1>\r\n<hr class=\"star-primary\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 text-center\">\r\n<h1>DEADLINES</h1>\r\n<hr class=\"star-primary\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<p><strong>Failure to complete the waiver by the dates below will result in the student being kept on the University health insurance plan for the remainder of that academic year and the applicable premium remaining on the student account!</strong> <br /><br /><strong>Waiver Deadline: </strong><br />Domestic Students on-line wavier: 