mic year and the applicable premium remaining on the student account!</strong> </span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Waiver Deadline: </strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Domestic Students on-line wavier: 10/10/2018</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Late waiver on-line with $50.00 late processing fee: 11/14/2018 </span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Coverage must have effective start date of 9/1/18 or before </span><br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Please Note: The University no longer generates a paper statement. Your Student Account Statement is by e-bill only. It is your responsibility to check your UB email. Failure to view your eBill details will not be accepted as a reason to waive the insurance charge after the published deadline.</strong></span></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">CONTACT US</span></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:separator --><hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" /><!-- /wp:separator -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Student Medical Insurance</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">1 Capen</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Univerity at Buffalo</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Buffalo, NY 14260-2100</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Phone: (716) 645-3036</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Fax: (716) 645-3465</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Email: asksmi@buffalo.edu</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>SBI Pharmacy</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">(716)-829-2368</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">D-17 Michael Hall</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">So