Y about benefits,<a href=\"https://www.bcbswny.com/content/WNYHome.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> click here</a>. </span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>All domestic waiver questions and concerns must be directed to: <a href=\"https://www.gallagherstudent.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">www.gallagherstudent.com</a> customer service at : <br />(877) 231-9757</strong> </span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>International Students/Scholars/OPT</strong> </span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">International students, Scholars, and OPT students have a global insurance policy available to them, contracted by SUNY through GeoBlue. To search for a provider, get detailed plan benefits or to contact GeoBlue directly, <a href=\"https://www.geobluestudents.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">click here. </a>Students and scholars who are adequately insured may be able to waive the GeoBlue insurance plan by providing proof of comparable coverage. Restrictions and deadlines apply.<a href=\"http://healthinsurance.buffalo.edu/insuranceforms.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">  Click here to access the wavier packet.</a></span><br /><br /></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">FALL 2018 INFORMATION IS COMING SOON</span></h1>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:separator --><hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" /><!-- /wp:separator -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1,\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">DEADLINES</span></h1>\r\n</br>\r\n</br>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:separator --><hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" /><!-- /wp:separator -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Failure to complete the waiver by the dates below will result in the student being kept on the University health insurance plan for the remainder of that academic year and the applicable premium remaining on the student account!</strong> </span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Waiver Deadline: </strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Domestic Students on-line wavier: 10/10/2018</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Late waiver on-line with $50.00 late processing fee: 11/14/2018 </span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Coverage must have effective start date of 9/1/18 or before </span><br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Please Note: The University no longer generates a paper statement. Your Student Account Statement is by e-bill only. It is your responsibility to check your UB email. Failure to view your eBill details will not be accepted as a reason to waive the insurance charge after the published deadline.</strong></span></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">CONTACT US</span></h2>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:separator --><hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" /><!-- /wp:separator -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Student Medical Insurance</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">1 Capen</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Univerity at Buffalo</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Buffalo, NY 14260-2100</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Phone: (716) 645-3036</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Fax: (716) 645-3465</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Email: asksmi@buffalo.edu</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>SBI Pharmacy</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">(716)-829-2368</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">D-17 Michael Hall</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">South Campus</span><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Domestic Insurance Providers:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Blue Cross Blue Shield</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">1-800-888-0757</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><a href=\"https://www.bcbswny.com/content/WNYHome.html\">Bcbswny.com</a></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Domestic Insurance Waiver Provider:</strong></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">Gallagher Student Health</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">1-877-231-9757</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><a href=\"http://healthinsurance.buffalo.edu/www.gallagherstudent.com\">www.gallagherstudent.com</a></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><strong>International Insurance Providers:</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">GeoBlue </span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\">1-844-268-2686</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 21px;\"><a href=\"http://healthinsurance.buffalo.edu/www.geobluestudents.com\">www.geobluestudents.com</a></span></p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'SBI Insurance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '428-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-25 15:34:43', '2018-08-25 15:34:43', '', 428, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/2018/08/25/428-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
